Original_Text:
CEPA 6 200608151



                                                    A bad holiday!


Every year, around summer time I spend my holiday in England, I go there to see my grandparents and some cousins. I like it there. I went there with my family and my freind who was  excited to comealong with us. We couldn't wait for the next day to come and leave away this hot weather. So we stayed up waiting for time to pass by, the next thing I see that we were late for our flight. So my parents took the first flight to england and we waited for the next.time passes by and our flight was soon to be ready to leave. We got on and ready to depart. The flight was horrable . there was many inneraction going on air addtion to the bad weather. finally we had arrived and glad to see my family . As for me at that moment looking at greens and small little houses along the way.
My freind and I couldn't wait to relax so we started going around the city. We got to london eye and went on the wheel . It suddenly stopped and we were on the top, it was ascary view and frightning. As we got down that was enough for the day. On the next day we went shopping , on our way there the car brokedown, so we had to take the trains. minutes later the electricity went off. It was soo dark that I lost my way. And from that same moment some one grabed me and stole my bag. I cried all night and day couse everything important was in it. I wept all week because of what happend days goes by. As soon as you knowing my  summer ended on our way back home in Dubai we has an accident that caused injuries to my brothers and back in England my grandmother passed away.Ooh!! that was one lousy and terribale holiday.

CEPA 5 200600411



Last year I spent my holiday in the Sudai Arabia, I went with my mother, father and 
sisters . We went by a plan , and we stayed there 1 month.
We stayed in a very nice hotel in Macca which called ( Abraj Macca ).
I had taken an Omra there,  and saw AlKaaba and when I saw it and prayed there I had felt  a very nice feeling. Also I asked Alla to help me in my life. Then we visited Al Madeena  which was a wonderful city , and saw the tomb of our Prophet Mohammed .
After that , we went to the capital of Sadui Arabai which called Al- Ryaad , where we stayed in it 1 week. The shopping there was very comfortable , so I bought a many and adress for 
my sister's wedding. Also i visited apark and taken a nice photos to be members for this 
time.
Finally, we come back to our lovely country with a nice gifts for our relatives here . And 
I hope to do it again one day .,because it is a wonderful holiday because I changed my 
behaviors and I feel now very pleased .
